Title: You're on the Essentials plan
Body: Welcome to Essentials. This free plan gives you the basics needed to be successful with OKRs.

Title: Activate username?
Body: They'll have access to your organization's files.

Title: Activate team?
Body: The team will be able to own OKRs.

Title: Deactivate username?
Body: Data related to this user will remain visible. They can be reactivated at any time.

Title: Deactivate team?
Body: Deactivated teams will still be visible, but can't own OKRs. You can reactivate the team at any time.

Title: Unauthorized access
Body: Authentication is required, please sign in.

Title: Confirm saving
Body: Please note that your existing Key Results will be deleted.

Title: Confirm moving Objective
Body: Moving this Objective will break the links of the contained Key Results. Once broken you can't recover them.

Title: This Key Result is dynamic
Body: If you decide to proceed with cascading, this Key Result will stop having dynamic progress.

Title: Delete username?
Body: Any data related to them will be deleted. This can't be undone.

Title: Delete custom field?
Body: This custom field is assigned to 11 amount of items. Once deleted the information will not be visible.

Title: Delete custom field?
Body: Once deleted you can't recover it.

Title: Delete connection?
Body: If you delete this connection data sources using this connection and their entities will be deleted too.

Title: Delete data source?
Body: If you delete this data source entities powered by this data source will be deleted too.

Title: Delete entity?
Body: If you delete this entity any insights using data from it will break. Also the dynamic Key Results based on the affected insights won’t update anymore. If you still want to delete the entity, please type its name in the input field below.

Title: Delete insightboard?
Body: Once deleted the insightboard can't be recovered.

Title: Delete insight?
Body: Once deleted the insight can't be recovered.

Title: Delete demo session?
Body: If you delete the session the Objectives that are in this session will be deleted and they could not be reverted.

Title: Delete session?
Body: If you delete the session the Objectives that are in it will be moved to 'Objectives without a session' under OKRs > Browse sessions > Objectives without a session. Once there, they cannot be edited but when moved back to a session, the alignment tree you had before will be reproduced as it was.

Title: Delete tag?
Body: This tag is being used in 42 OKRs, Insightboards or reports. By deleting it, all data will be lost. This action is irreversible!

Title: Forbidden
Body: You don't have the neccessary permissions. Please contact your account administrator.

Title: Item not found
Body: The item you are looking for might be deleted or with restricted access. Please make sure the URL is correct.

Title: Item can't be modified
Body: The item you are trying to modify is locked. Please unlock it first.

Title: Request was denied
Body: There are some network connectivity issues. This could be caused by temporary network failure with your Internet connection. If this message persists appearing and you are using any security tool, please consider adding an exception for 'gtmhub.com'. Remember that Gtmhub does not serve any ads, nor anything else to disturb your privacy.
An unexpected error has occurred.

Title: Login error
Body: There has been an error entering from the invite link.

Title: Login error
Body: You’re not invited to the account you’re trying to log into. If you have an account with 'gtmhub.com' please try logging with it. If not contact support.

Title: Server error
Body: We are experiencing issues with our servers. Try to refresh the page or try again later.

Title: Action not supported
Body: This action isn't supported by this trigger. Only actions that are supported by this trigger will be executed.
